#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.report_fiscal_attestation_document
msgid "31.05"
msgstr "31.05"

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. <strong>Involve Volunteers</strong>: Create volunteer roles in Employees "
"and assign\n"
"            shifts using Planning."
msgstr ""
"4. <strong>Impliquez les bénévoles</strong> : créez des rôles de bénévoles "
"dans l'app Employés et assignez\n"
"     des créneaux à l'aide de l'app Planification."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5.<strong> Sell Campaign Merchandise</strong>: Offer items like a <em>“Stop "
"Child\n"
"                Labor” badge</em> via eCommerce, and manage orders and "
"payments online."
msgstr ""
"5. <strong>Vendez des produits de campagne</strong> : proposez des articles "
"comme un <em>badge \"Stop Child Labor\"</em> via l'eCommerce, et gérez les "
"commandes et les paiements en ligne."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"6. <strong>Track Costs</strong>: Log campaign-related expenses in Expenses, "
"linked to the\n"
"            project."
msgstr ""
"6. <strong>Suivez les coûts</strong> : enregistrez les dépenses liées à la "
"campagne dans l’application Notes de frais, liées au projet."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"7. <strong>Send Attestations</strong>: Generate and sign donation "
"attestations using\n"
"            Donations and Sign, then send to supporters and authorities at "
"the end of the year."
msgstr ""
"7. <strong>Envoyez les attestations</strong> : générez et signez des "
"attestations fiscales de don à l’aide de Donations et Signature, puis "
"envoyez-les aux donateurs et aux autorités en fin d’année."

#. module: non_profit_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:non_profit_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"8. <strong>Keep Supporters Engaged</strong>: Use Email Marketing to send "
"updates and\n"
"            thank-you messages to donors and petition signers."
msgstr ""
"8. <strong>Fidélisez vos soutiens</strong> : utilisez E-mail Marketing pour "
"envoyer des mises à jour et des messages de remerciement aux donateurs et "
"aux signataires de pétitions."

