msgid ""
"As a member, you become part of a network of committed\n"
"                                    individuals who believe in justice not "
"as an idea, but as a\n"
"                                    lived reality; on the ground, in policy, "
"in schools, and on the\n"
"                                    streets. Your membership helps us "
"advocate with strength,\n"
"                                    mobilize with courage, and educate with "
"heart."
msgstr ""
"En tant que membre, vous rejoignez un réseau de personnes engagées qui "
"considèrent la justice non comme une simple idée, mais comme une réalité "
